            "answer_text": "Lots of different reasons for different songs and different songwriters. Some possibilities: Drugs.Songwriter is more melody/sound oriented and leaves lyrics til last/doesn't care that they don't make sense. It's about feelings/emotions not thoughts. Like word art in audio form.Songwriting is about connecting dots, allowing your mind to leap. The best songwriters can help others connect those same dots, to see the connections. Sometimes it doesn't quite come off. Sometimes songwriters don't care if everyone gets it.",
